description: A sinkhole swallowed a car in Minnesota, just west of Minneapolis.
maintext: A sinkhole swallowed a car in Minnesota, just west of Minneapolis.The road opened up yesterday in Redwood Falls after some heavy rain.The driver was a 16-year-old who had only had his license for about a month.The teen says he had to climb out a back window.He wasn't hurt, thanks to his seat belt and airbag.
title: Sinkhole opens up, swallows car after heavy rain in Minnesota
